d; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Man City vs Liverpool t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 C1/ Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n- Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u00fap C1/ Champions League l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 10 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Ch\u1ec9 duy nh\u1ea5t 1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong t\u1ed1p 4 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n Liverpool \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Man United (12 l\u1ea7n).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong ke sau tran dau Man City vs Liverpool tu ket luot ve C1 hinh anh\" title=\"Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Man City vs Liverpool t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 C1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/Firmino-ghi-ban-cho-Liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Firmino \u0103n m\u1eebng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Man City vs Liverpool t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 C1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n- Sau khi l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League trong 7 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch HLV Barcelona v\u00e0 Bayern Munich, Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y trong c\u1ea3 2 m\u00f9a \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i Man City.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/ket-qua-man-city-vs-liverpool-tran-dau-tu-ket-champions-league-201718-184-183969.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Liverpool th\u1eafng Man City 3-0</strong></span> v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng do Pep Guardiola d\u1eabn d\u1eaft 3 l\u1ea7n trong m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- H\u1eadu th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Man City vs Liverpool t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 C1, Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Pep Guardiola nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 HLV n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c (7 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Roberto Firmino v\u00e0 Mohamed Salah \u0111\u00e3 ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i c\u00fap C1/ Champions League h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai kh\u00e1c trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Liverpool (c\u00f9ng 8 b\u00e0n).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Salah \u0111\u00e3 tham gia tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o 50 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Liverpool tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00f9a n\u00e0y (39 b\u00e0n, 11 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ghi 33 b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i Champions League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- B\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a Gabriel Jesus <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/truc-tiep-man-city-vs-liverpool-01h45-ngay-114-champions-league-201718-372-183965.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Man City vs Liverpool t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 C1</strong></span> di\u1ec5n ra ch\u1ec9 sau 1 ph\u00fat 56 gi\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so Man City 1-2 Liverpool\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 Man City 1-2 Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/Man-City-1-2-(1-5)-Liverpool-Sap-mat-tren-san-nha,-Man-xanh-cui-dau-roi-khoi-Champions-League-hinh-anh-goc-2.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 sau tr\u1eadn Man City 1-2 Liverpool</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Champions League tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ha-guc-man-city-liverpool-ha-not-man-utd-184-183978.html\">H\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Man City, Liverpool h\u1ea1 n\u1ed1t\u2026 Man Utd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/thay-gi-sau-man-nguoc-dong-khong-tuong-cua-roma-truoc-barca-184-183976.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau m\u00e0n ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Roma tr\u01b0\u1edbc Barca?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/tranh-cai-tran-man-city-12-liverpool-leroy-sane-da-viet-vi-hay-chua-184-183975.html\">Tranh c\u00e3i tr\u1eadn Man City 1-2 Liverpool: Leroy Sane \u0111\u00e3 vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb hay ch\u01b0a?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ket-qua-man-city-vs-liverpool-tran-dau-tu-ket-champions-league-201718-184-183969.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Man City vs Liverpool tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ket-qua-roma-vs-barca-tran-dau-tu-ket-champions-league-201718-184-183967.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Roma vs Barca tr\u1e