p 4 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 tham d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ed1 1 ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c m\u00f9a t\u1edbi, song ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eden Hazard v\u1eabn b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1c quan v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Chelsea.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hazard vs Barca\" title=\"Hazard vs Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/15/hazard-bi-loai-khoi-champions-league-tot-cho-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3><em>Hazard v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra l\u1ea1c quan sau khi Chelsea&nbsp;b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng Champions League</em></h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 s\u1ed1 10 cho r\u1eb1ng: &quot;\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n Chelsea g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf Champions League m\u1ed7i n\u0103m. N\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 Champions League v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec v\u1eady, \u0111\u00f4i khi m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 k\u00e9m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00e1c t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n...Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n FA cup v\u00e0 t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Chelsea s\u1ebd mang chi\u1ebfc cup n\u00e0y v\u1ec1 Stamford Bridge v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a d\u00e0nh t\u1eb7ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9&quot;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi Chelsea. &ldquo;M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 thua nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn theo c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U v\u00e0 Tottenham, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. \u0110\u00e2y qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i&quot;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ebft b\u00e1t, l\u00fac n\u00e0y, Hazard v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ea5u danh hi\u1ec7u l\u00e0 FA Cup. Theo l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Southamton v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 22/4 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1015","checkdouble":"183970"},{"date":"23:01 10/04","title":"B\u00e1o Ph\u00e1p h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ebd r\u1eddi M.U trong h\u00e8 t\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/8/bao-phap-he-lo-ngoi-sao-se-roi-mu-trong-he-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margi