:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Link xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs N\u1eef Australia: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn ch\u00ednh, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e8m link xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Australia di\u1ec5n ra l\u00fac 0h \u0111\u00eam ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 11/4.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00fang nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i VCK Asian Cup 2018 (gi\u1ea3i c\u00f3 t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2019) \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng t\u1eed th\u1ea7n, g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Australia v\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng do tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch, tuy\u1ec3n n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-4. Thua \u0111\u1eadm nh\u01b0ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 World Cup, n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t \u1edf hai tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u l\u1ec7 gi\u1ea3i quy \u0111\u1ecbnh hai \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec m\u1ed7i b\u1ea3ng s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi 2019. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng ba c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn play-off tranh v\u00e9 v\u1edbt t\u1edbi World Cup.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Link xem truc tiep Nu Viet Nam vs Nu Australia hom nay 114 hinh anh\" title=\"Link xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs N\u1eef Australia h\u00f4m nay 114 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/10/tuyen-nu-viet-nam-vs-australia-tim-ve-du-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs N\u1eef Australia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Austrlia, HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh: \u201cAustralia l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh, s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 l\u00e0 l\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o World Cup l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb \u00e1p l\u1ef1c g\u00ec c\u1ea3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m cao nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, tuy\u1ec3n n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Australia t\u1eebng g\u1eb7p nhau nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n. N\u1ebfu thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00fang s\u1ee9c, c\u00e1c c\u00f4 g\u00e1i \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn quy\u1ebft chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u01b0\u1ee3t cu\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1eefa tuy\u1ec3n n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Australia s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 0 gi\u1edd ng\u00e0y 11/4 (theo gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam) tr\u00ean s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf Amman, Jordan.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Link xem truc tiep Nu Viet Nam vs Nu Australia hom nay 114 hinh anh\" title=\"Link xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs N\u1eef Australia h\u00f4m nay 114 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/10/BXH.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs N\u1eef Australia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1012","checkdouble":"183962"},{"date":"20:10 10/04","title":"VPF \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n n\u1ebfu b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecf V-League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/10/4/vpf-da-co-phuong-an-neu-bau-duc-bo-vleague.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margi