5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 Man City vs Liverpool, c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 \u00edt c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pep Guardiola l\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ebf c\u1edd. CLB d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u Premier League \u0111ang \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1 bay kh\u1ecfi Cup C1.</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>L\u1ee3i th\u1ebf qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a Liverpool</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 3 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1, \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean The Kop kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n chi\u1ebfc v\u00e9 n\u1eafm trong tay m\u00ecnh l\u1ea1i bay m\u1ea5t. D\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i Etihad v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay, nh\u01b0ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Jurgen Klopp \u0111i ti\u1ebfp l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t m\u00e0 h\u1ecd t\u1ea1o ra \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Man City vs Liverpool.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, <strong>L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n &ldquo;thua nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng&rdquo; 2 b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ea1i</strong>. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p h\u1ecd th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu ghi 3 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean (v\u00ed d\u1ee5 3-6), Top 4 \u0111\u1ed9i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t Champions League c\u0169ng s\u1ebd ghi danh Liverpool. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Man xanh c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i n\u00e3 v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng, m\u1ed9t ng\u1ecdn n\u00fai qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1eafng, m\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ee9c \u00e9p kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pep Guardiola. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed n\u1ebfu th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc (\u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra), \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad ph\u1ea3i ghi 4 b\u00e0n. V\u00e0 theo c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Frank Lampard, <strong>Liverpool s\u1ebd b\u1ecb&hellip; c\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t trong th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 Man xanh l\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ebf c\u1edd.</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man City vs Liverpool Nhung ly do Klopp-team se di tiep hinh anh\" title=\"Man City vs Liverpool Nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do Klopp-team s\u1ebd \u0111i ti\u1ebfp h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/10/live.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool \u0111ang n\u1eafm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>S\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Salah</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a v\u1ecb vua Ai C\u1eadp v\u1edbi The Kop, khi Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c h\u1eb3n trong <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/diem-nhan-tran-everton-00-liverpool-172-183778.html\" target=\"_blank\">tr\u1eadn derby Merseyside nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n</span> cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n v\u1eeba qua khi thi\u1ebfu anh. Nh\u01b0ng theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, &ldquo;Th\u00e1nh Salah&rdquo; \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u00e3 ghi 1 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 1 pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Pep Guardiola b\u1ed1i r\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn n\u01a1i h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u1eed huy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 Salah d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng khai th\u00e1c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n nh\u1edb, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 &ldquo;ch\u1eafc c\u1ed1p&rdquo; v\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn Aymeric Laporte \u0111\u00e1 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Premier League. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Fabian Delph l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ed1t trong t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 so v\u1edbi Laporte khi ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Man City ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu sai l\u1ea7m trong c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 (Laporte hay Delph), kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng h\u1ecd b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i m\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 v\u00ec <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/salah-binh-phuc-chan-thuong-truoc-them-dai-chien-man-city-184-183907.html\" target=\"_blank\">Mohamed Salah tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</span>, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn c\u01a1n \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Pep Guardiola.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Salah da tro lai trong tran Man City vs Liverpool\" title=\"Salah \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn Man City vs Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/10/salah.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Salah s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn Man City vs Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>N\u1ed7i \u00e1m \u1ea3nh Man United</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div>Sau khi th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool, Man xanh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i tinh th\u1ea7n trong tr\u1eadn derby Manchester cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc. M\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi h\u1ecd trong&hellip; n\u1eeda tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, khi Man City thi\u1ebfu nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf, v\u00e0 s\u1edbm c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Tuy nhi\u00ean ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn n\u1eeda xanh s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i 2 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad \u0111ang \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng. \u0110\u00e0nh r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd l\u00e0m g\u00ec, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi t\u00e2m l\u00fd n\u1eb7ng tr\u0129u v\u1edbi Liverpool, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3n t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, n\u1ed7i \u00e1m \u1ea3nh mang t\u00ean MU l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 cho The Kop, khi h\u1ecd th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng s\u01a1 h\u1edf trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Man xanh. V\u1edbi h\u00e0ng t\u00e1 &ldquo;v\u0169 kh\u00ed h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t&rdquo; trong tay, Jurgen Klopp lu\u00f4n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn Man City b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, qua \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ec5 \u0111o\u00e1n h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tuyen giua cua MU da toa sang trong tran dau Man City vs MU\" title=\"Tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a MU \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Man City vs MU\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/tiet-lo-bat-ngo-ve-nguoi-hung-cua-mu-trong-tran-derby.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc MU khi\u1ebfn Man City g\u1eb7p kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>H\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 The Kop</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">14 &ndash; \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 con s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Liverpool kh\u00f4ng th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi qu\u00e1 3 b\u00e0n/tr\u1eadn. \u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Man City, nh\u01b0ng tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn 4 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u1edf chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i. C\u00f2n n\u1ebfu t\u00ednh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Liverpool thua \u0111\u1eadm tr\u00ean 3 b\u00e0n, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y m\u1edbi xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n 1 l\u1ea7n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, khi h\u1ecd thua ch\u00ednh Man City 0-5 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Premier League.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 v\u1eady, ai c\u0169ng hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng Liverpool l\u00fac n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ng\u00e2y th\u01a1 trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y c\u00f3 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n l\u1edbn b\u1edfi Liverpool b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t ng\u01b0\u1eddi (Sadio Mane nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf). Ch\u1ee9 n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 thi \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Man City l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh t\u00edch n\u00e0y. N\u1ebfu nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, Man xanh c\u0169ng b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 1 b\u00e0n danh d\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u01a1n n\u1eefa bom t\u1ea5n Virgil Van Dijk \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, v\u00e0 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield. Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Loris Karius \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u1edf khung th\u00e0nh, c\u0169ng \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu phong \u0111\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man City vs Liverpool Van Dijk va Jesus\" title=\"Man City vs Liverpool Van Dijk va Jesus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/Man-City-vs-Liverpool-Van-Dijk-va-Jesus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf \u0111ang n\u1eb1m trong tay Jurgen Klopp, khi \u00f4ng c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n th\u1ee7 h\u00f2a l\u00e0 c\u1ea7m ch\u1eafc chi\u1ebfc v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Tuy nhi\u00ean, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/man-city-vs-liverpool-1h45-ngay-114-con-nuoc-con-tat-184-183914.html\" target=\"_blank\">Man City vs Liverpool</span> v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng theo d\u00f5i, b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 2 CLB s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t Premier League v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 1h45 r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng mai, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tin t\u1ee9c li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n</strong> <br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/lampard-man-city-van-con-co-hoi-truoc-liverpool-184-183945.html\">Lampard: Man City v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/pep-man-city-phai-co-tran-dau-hoan-hao-truoc-liverpool-184-183923.html\">Pep ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 Man City v\u01b0\u1ee3t \u1ea3i Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/klopp-man-city-dang-ra-phai-thang-mu-den-60-184-183906.html\">Klopp: &ldquo;Man City \u0111\u00e1ng ra ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng MU \u0111\u1ebfn 6-0&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/sao-man-city-to-liverpool-su-dung-chien-thuat-tieu-cuc-184-183905.html\">Sao Man City t\u1ed1 Liverpool s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/riise-liverpool-se-loai-man-city-va-vo-dich-champions-league-184-183876.html\">Riise: Liverpool s\u1ebd lo\u1ea1i Man City v\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-va-van-de-harry-kane-cua-rieng-minh-172-183795.html\">Liverpool v\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 Harry Kane c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1008","checkdouble":"183957"},{"date":"18:38 10/04","title":"Man City vs Liverpool: 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/8/man-city-vs-liverpool-5-cau-thu-co-the-dinh-doat-tran-dau.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin: