r-tr{border-top-right-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-bl{border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Man City vs Liverpool t\u1ea1i Etihad s\u1eafp t\u1edbi h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn khi \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y v\u00e0o th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f9ng. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft \u0111\u00eam nay.</h2>\r\n<h2>Dejan Loven</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch t\u1eeb c\u00e1c C\u0110V Liverpool v\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng Lovren \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City t\u1ea1i Anfield c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 1 tu\u1ea7n. Anh t\u1ecf ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ef1 tin khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u00ean ph\u00eda The Citizens. Lovren gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i trong m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i pha kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn quan tr\u1ecdng c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i s\u00e1ng su\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Joel Matip b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Lovren coi nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Van Dijk \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Liverpool. V\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao 28 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 t\u00e2m l\u00fd th\u00e9p nh\u01b0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n c\u01a1n cu\u1ed3ng phong Man City \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng khoan nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Georginio Wijnaldum\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tran dau Man City vs Liverpool 5 cau thu dinh doat tran dau hinh anh\" title=\"Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Man City vs Liverpool 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/7/19/Tran-dau-Man-City-vs-Liverpool-5-cau-thu-dinh-doat-tran-dau-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Wijnaldum l\u00e0 c\u1ee9u c\u00e1nh \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 cho Klopp \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Man City vs Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/man-city-vs-liverpool-1h45-ngay-114-con-nuoc-con-tat-184-183914.html\" target=\"_blank\">tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Man City vs Liverpool</span> s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, The&nbsp;Kop s\u1ebd thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Jordan Henderson v\u00e0 Emre Can cho tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 \u1edf Etihad. Nh\u1edd v\u1eady, Wijnaldum coi nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t v\u00e0 gi\u00fap Liverpool \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng t\u1ea1i Manchester.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 H\u00e0 Lan c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t trong tr\u1eadn derby Merseyside cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua. Anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn. Gini ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c trung tuy\u1ebfn v\u00e0 t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 k\u1ec3. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Wijnaldum c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea cho th\u1ea5y, anh \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c t\u1edbi 94% tr\u01b0\u1edbc Everton.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nWijnaldum s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t vai tr\u00f2 l\u1edbn \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Man City s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. Anh c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n Kevin De Bruyne v\u00e0 David Silva, nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c, Wijnaldum c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Liverpool ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn thua tanh b\u00e0nh v\u00e0 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi Champions League.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/man-city-vs-liverpool-1h45-ngay-114-con-nuoc-con-tat-184-183914.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/10/man-city-vs-liverpool-1h45-ngay-114-con-nuoc-con-tat.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/man-city-vs-liverpool-1h45-ngay-114-con-nuoc-con-tat-184-183914.html\">Man City vs Liverpool (1h45 ng\u00e0y 11/4): C\u00f2n n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f2n t\u00e1t</span><br>\r\n<span>B\u01b0\u1edbc ra th\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ecba Etihad cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn sinh t\u1eed Man City vs Liverpool v\u1edbi t\u00e2m l\u00fd m\u00f4ng lung kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c t\u1ea1o n\u00ean ph\u00e9p m\u00e0u n\u00e0o hay kh\u00f4ng, nh\u1eefng g\u00ec...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>David Silva</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Silva l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Man City trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Pep Guardiola, Silva c\u00f2n tr\u1edf n\u00ean nguy hi\u1ec3m h\u01a1n khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i t\u1ea1i Anfield. Anh \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool. Nh\u01b0ng Silva v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u1ef1ng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn. V\u00ec v\u1eady, anh v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Man City t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Silva l\u00e0 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. N\u1ebfu c\u1ef1u binh c\u1ee7a Man City ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00fang s\u1ee9c, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ghi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Liverpool kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kevin De Bruyne\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool vs Man City De Bruyne va Can\" title=\"Liverpool vs Man City De Bruyne va Can\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/mac-thua-tham-sao-man-city-van-bao-ve-cdv-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>De Bruyne \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Man City m\u1edf kh\u00f3a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">De Bruyne \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p m\u1edbi \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o ch\u00ednh trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola. T\u00ednh ri\u00eang \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i Premier League, De Bruyne \u0111\u00e3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edbi 15 l\u1ea7n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Chelsea c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 David Silva, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i. Nh\u01b0ng \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1, h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Liverpool ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00f9i l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1eddng quy\u1ec1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t cho Man City. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u00f3, De Bruyne s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 suy t\u00ednh t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n x\u00e9 toang h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. V\u1eady n\u00ean, m\u1ed7i khi De Bruyne c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Liverpool c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung h\u1ebft m\u1ee9c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Virgil van Dijk</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/van-dijk-khong-ngu-duoc-sau-tran-thang-man-city-184-183930.html\" target=\"_blank\">Van Dijk</span> \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3m t\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a NHM Liverpool v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 c\u1ea3ng ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVan Dijk l\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 \u0111ang ch\u1ee9ng minh r\u1eb1ng anh x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi t\u1eebng xu m\u00e0 The Kop b\u1ecf ra. \u0110\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 r\u00e0o c\u1ea3n l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 Man City bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cho \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola c\u00f3 l\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u00fat. T\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n H\u00e0 Lan mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh cho nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xung quanh nh\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ec9 huy tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 then ch\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a Liverpool kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi m\u00e0 c\u00f2n trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Man City vs Liverpool:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nhung-ly-do-liverpool-se-vuot-qua-man-city-de-lot-vao-ban-ket-184-183957.html\">Nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do Liverpool s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Man City \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/van-dijk-khong-ngu-duoc-sau-tran-thang-man-city-184-183930.html\">Van Dijk kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/pep-man-city-phai-co-tran-dau-hoan-hao-truoc-liverpool-184-183923.html\">Pep ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 Man City v\u01b0\u1ee3t \u1ea3i Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/klopp-canh-bao-cac-hoc-tro-truoc-dai-chien-voi-man-city-184-183920.html\">Klopp c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/salah-binh-phuc-chan-thuong-truoc-them-dai-chien-man-city-184-183907.html\">Super Salah tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/klopp-man-city-dang-ra-phai-thang-mu-den-60-184-183906.html\">Klopp: &ldquo;Man City \u0111\u00e1ng ra ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng MU \u0111\u1ebfn 6-0&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (Bongda24h)</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1007","checkdouble":"183958"},{"date":"19:28 10/04","title":"