display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n trung v\u1ec7 Samuel Umtiti r\u1eddi Barca \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n t\u00e1n li\u00ean t\u1ee5c trong th\u1eddi gian qua. H\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea1i gia r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y trong khi Barcelona \u0111ang b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n anh.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Umtiti \u0111\u00ecnh tr\u1ec7</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Samuel Umtiti gia nh\u1eadp Barcelona t\u1eeb Lyon m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2016. Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Barca kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u1edd r\u1eb1ng trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 nhanh \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. H\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 th\u00f2ng v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Umtiti \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u Euro (52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u00ednh giao k\u00e8o n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 bom n\u1ed5 ch\u1eadm khi\u1ebfn l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Barca lo n\u01a1m n\u1edbp. H\u1ecd lo l\u1eafng r\u1eb1ng trong th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean phi m\u00e3, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/tu-choi-cam-ket-voi-barca-umtiti-se-sang-man-united-172-182867.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>trung v\u1ec7 Samuel Umtiti r\u1eddi Barca</strong></span> kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i qu\u00e1 xa v\u1eddi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Dau hieu lon trung ve Samuel Umtiti roi Barca hinh anh\" title=\"D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn trung v\u1ec7 Samuel Umtiti r\u1eddi Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/10/day-dau-hieu-lon-cho-thay-trung-ve-samuel-umtiti-den-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng trung v\u1ec7 Samuel Umtiti r\u1eddi Barca \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBarca r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n m\u1ed9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Umtiti m\u00e0 m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh l\u1ea1i ph\u00ed ra \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00fac m\u1eafc n\u1eb1m \u1edf ch\u1ed7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00ean g\u1ea5p 3 l\u1ea7n hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, t\u1ee9c 9 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t khi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Camp Nou ch\u00f9n tay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia Anh h\u0103m h\u1edf</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng trung v\u1ec7 Samuel Umtiti r\u1eddi Barca \u0111ang l\u1edbn d\u1ea7n, c\u00e1c \u00f4ng l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i Premier League \u0111ang t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t s\u1ed1t s\u1eafng. Theo t\u1edd Diario Gol, \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean g\u1ed3m Man United, Chelsea, Arsenal, Liverpool v\u00e0 Man City mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Lyon trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-vuot-mat-mu-vu-trung-ve-barca-172-181704.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/4/24/chelsea-muon-vuot-mat-mu-vu-trung-ve-barca.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-vuot-mat-mu-vu-trung-ve-barca-172-181704.html\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t M.U v\u1ee5 trung v\u1ec7 Barca</span><br>\r\n<span>Chelsea mua trung v\u1ec7 Samuel Umtiti c\u1ee7a Barca l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Don Balon c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin &ldquo;s\u1ed1t d\u1ebbo&rdquo; t\u1eeb T\u00e2y Ban Nha khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua: Umtiti \u0111\u00e3 t\u00e2m s\u1ef1 v\u1edbi \u0111\u00e0n anh Gerard Pique r\u1eb1ng anh \u0111ang ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n sang Premier League thi \u0111\u1ea5u. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, Barca kh\u00f4ng thi\u1ebfu tham v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Umtiti chinh ph\u1ee5c c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u. Nh\u01b0ng xem ra ch\u1ec9 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1m l\u1ef1c t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh h\u00f9ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y th\u00f4ng tin <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/chot-thoi-gian-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai-umtiti-180-183673.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Umtiti s\u1ebd ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 5</strong></span> t\u1edbi l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c. D\u0129 nhi\u00ean, CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh trung v\u1ec7 Samuel Umtiti r\u1eddi Barca. Nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00e1ch th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n, Barca s\u1ebd b\u1ecf ti\u1ec1n mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch h\u1ecd quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Dayot Upamecano l\u00e0 v\u00ed d\u1ee5.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-chao-gia-soc-cho-hau-ve-vo-danh-180-183910.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/10/barca-chao-gia-soc-cho-hau-ve-vo-danh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-chao-gia-soc-cho-hau-ve-vo-danh-180-183910.html\">Barca ch\u00e0o gi\u00e1 s\u1ed1c cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 v\u00f4 danh</span><br>\r\n<span>Dayot Upamecano n\u1ed5i l\u00ean trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o RB Leipzig trong 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, vi\u1ec7c Barca mua trung v\u1ec7 Upamecano v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u1eabn khi\u1ebfn cho...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea v\u1ec1 Samuel Umtiti:</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/96547-41198/033100\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Samuel Umtiti</span><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-chao-gia-soc-cho-hau-ve-vo-danh-180-183910.html\">Barca ch\u00e0o gi\u00e1 s\u1ed1c cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 v\u00f4 danh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-nhin-bao-gio-messi-thanh-liet-si-cua-barca-180-183894.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Bao gi\u1edd Messi th\u00e0nh &ldquo;li\u1ec7t s\u0129&rdquo; c\u1ee7a Barca?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-dang-dam-phan-chieu-mo-sao-mu-180-183720.html\">Barca \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chuyen-nhuong-barca-khong-mua-verratti-180-183658.html\">Barca s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng nh\u1ea3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-nghi-ra-cach-de-so-huu-luke-shaw-180-183654.html\">Barca ngh\u0129 ra c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu Luke Shaw?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1003","checkdouble":"183956"},{"date":"18:50 10/04","title":"5 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn derby Manchester","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/10/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-4-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-derby-manchester.png","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right: