rgin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Man City \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 2-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Man City vs MU v\u00f2ng 33 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</h2>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Alexis Sanchez</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alexis Sanchez ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 trung t\u00e2m trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y trong c\u1ea3 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. \u1ede b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Sanchez \u0111i b\u00f3ng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c b\u00ean c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i, anh l\u1eadt b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o trong \u0111\u1ec3 Ander Herrera ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho Pogba ghi b\u00e0n.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man City vs MU vong 33 Ngoai hang Anh hinh anh\" title=\"Man City vs MU v\u00f2ng 33 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/10/Man-City-vs-MU-vong-33-Ngoai-hang-Anh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sanchez g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y trong c\u1ea3 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n nh\u00e3n quan chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt s\u1eafc b\u00e9n khi tung m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00e0i chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 Pogba l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2 hi\u1ec7n t\u00ean l\u00ean b\u1ea3ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSanchez k\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u0103ng hoa b\u1eb1ng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng treo b\u00f3ng \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u01a1i \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ec3 trung v\u1ec7 Chris Smalling b\u0103ng v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec7m b\u00f3ng c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-2 cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1eeb khi chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Old Trafford v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m nay, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/du-am-man-city-23-mu-cau-tra-loi-cua-alexis-sanchez-172-183870.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Sanchez t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1</strong></span> trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn. Anh \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua cu\u1ed9c: Pep Guardiola</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Anfield, \u00f4ng g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c khi \u0111\u1ec3 Kevin de Bruyne ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Jesus v\u00e0 Aguero ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"5 nguoi chien thang va 4 nguoi that bai sau tran derby Manchester hinh anh 2\" title=\"5 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn derby Manchester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/10/5-nguoi-chien-thang-va-4-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-derby-Manchester-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pep c\u00f9ng Man City nh\u1eadn tr\u1eadn thua th\u1ee9 2 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nS\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Pep \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn M.U b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, b\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng l\u00e0 trong 30 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn Man City ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Nh\u01b0ng sang hi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 \u00f4ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1eeb ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM.U th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng treo b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m Man City \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, c\u1ea3 3 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng m\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i. Pep \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Man \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 3-2 \u00f4ng v\u1ed9i v\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0a b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng De Bruyne, Jesus v\u00e0 Aguero v\u00e0o s\u00e2n nh\u01b0ng Man City kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ebf c\u1edd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Paul Pogba</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Paul Pogba b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, anh th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Mourinho v\u00e0 t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch ra \u0111i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Nh\u01b0ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ngo\u00e0i tai nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba toa sang voi mot cu dup\" title=\"Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/10/pogba.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng 2 ph\u00fat (t\u1eeb ph\u00fat 53 \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 55). 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n h\u1ebft nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd trong tranh ch\u1ea5p, tinh t\u1ebf v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPogba d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 3 l\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c 100% v\u00e0 mang v\u1ec1 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Etihad gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 khen ng\u1ee3i r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Mourinho.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua cu\u1ed9c: Chris Smalling</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chris Smalling ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda M.U trong hi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i chung v\u1edbi Eric Bailly trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7. C\u1ef1u sao Fulham c\u0169ng m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i trong c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Smalling mac sai lam trong 2 ban thua cua M.U\" title=\"Smalling m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m trong 2 b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a M.U\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/10/smalling.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Smalling m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m trong 2 b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u1ede b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Kompany, ch\u00ednh Smalling l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ecb trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Man City \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng tranh ch\u1ea5p tr\u00ean kh\u00f4ng, c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Kompany qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c khi\u1ebfn De Gea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua th\u1ee9 2, Smaling l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 Gundogan v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c khi\u1ebfn De Gea ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2 v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Smalling lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean b\u1ecb\u00a0\u0111\u01b0a\u00a0v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch thanh l\u00fd \u1edf m\u1ed7i k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Chris Smalling</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch t\u1eeb t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng ch\u1ec9 trong m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc, v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Smalling th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n. Ch\u1eb3ng ai c\u00f2n nh\u1edb \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i trong hi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean khi anh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00fap Man \u0111\u1ecf mang v\u1ec1 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Smalling toa sang mang ve 3 diem cho Quy do\" title=\"Smalling t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng mang v\u1ec1 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/10/smalling2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Smalling t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng mang v\u1ec1 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nT\u1eeb t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Sanchez, Smalling b\u0103ng xu\u1ed1ng ch\u1ecdn ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u01a1i c\u1ee7a tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng, c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly g\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a anh khi\u1ebfn Ederson kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn khi Man City d\u1ed3n l\u00ean t\u00ecm b\u00e0n g\u1ee1, s\u1ee9c \u00e9p r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o ra v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Smalling c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua cu\u1ed9c: Raheem Sterling</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Jesus v\u00e0 Aguero \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, Sterling ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Man City. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh r\u1ea5t ch\u1ecbu kh\u00f3 di chuy\u1ec3n, anh c\u0169ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a s\u1ed1 7 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sterling bo lo 3 co hoi ngon an\" title=\"Sterling b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/10/sterling.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sterling b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nRaheem Sterling ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda Man City trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi M.U, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u00f3 3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi David de Gea nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n2 trong 3 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn trong 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu Sterling t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 4-0 sau hi\u1ec7p 1, khi \u0111\u00f3 k\u1ebft c\u1ee5c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Man Ciy vs MU v\u00f2ng 33 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, ch\u00ednh vi\u1ec7c Sterling b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Man City th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: David De Gea</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n David de Gea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Man City. Ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u00e1t b\u00f3ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 Gundogan n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-0 th\u00ec m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"De Gea choi rat tot trong tran Man City vs MU vong 33 Ngoai hang Anh\" title=\"De Gea ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong tr\u1eadn Man City vs MU v\u00f2ng 33 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/10/de-gea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>De Gea ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong tr\u1eadn Man City vs MU v\u00f2ng 33 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 4 l\u1ea7n c\u1ee9u thua, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1eefng c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 t\u1eeb ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, De Gea c\u00f2n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ch\u1ed7 d\u1ef1a cho h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1990 cho th\u1ea5y anh x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua cu\u1ed9c: Martin Atkinson</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Martin Atkinson \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u sau nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh trong tr\u1eadn Man City vs MU v\u00f2ng 33 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. NHM Man xanh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh kh\u00f4ng cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng 1 qu\u1ea3 11m.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Martin Atkinson bi chi trich rat nhieu\" title=\"Martin Atkinson b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/10/trong-tai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Martin Atkinson b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Ashley Young c\u00f3 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o v\u1edbi Sergio Aguero trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m, t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd ra Man City ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, nh\u01b0ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh l\u1ea1i n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u00ean ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng bi\u00ean Pep \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Atkinson l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Man City nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Liverpool</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a Man City \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u01a1i b\u00e0y trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi M.U. Liverpool ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i, b\u1edfi h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League v\u1edbi Man xanh ngay sau \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Klopp la nguoi vui nhat khi chung kien Man City that bai truoc M.U\" title=\"Klopp l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi vui nh\u1ea5t khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Man City th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/10/liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Klopp l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi vui nh\u1ea5t khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Man City th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nThe Kop c\u00f2n h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i khi Man City b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Etihad v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u0103ng c\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 t\u00e2m l\u00fd v\u00e0 t\u00e2m tr\u1ea1ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t. 2 tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Man City c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Video Man City 2-3 MU (V\u00f2ng 33 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2017/18)<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_265774\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/04/08/highlight-man-city-vs-man-utd-vong-33-nha.mp4&autoplay=false\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1002","checkdouble":"183959"}]}